{"word":"χραίνω","slug":"χραίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χραίνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:χράω'><el>χράω1</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to touch slightly</i>, <el>ὀλιγάκις ἄστυ χραίνων</el>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> keeping aloof from it, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to stain, spot, defile</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>;— <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> of moral pollution, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>χεῖρα χραίνεσθαι φόνωι</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be defiled</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}